info.name: Desi Malai Stick Kulfi
info.description: Serves 1 | The classic, authentic, rustic avatar of your favourite kulfi, in form of easy-to-devour slices. This one has been custom-made to deliver creamy perfection. Kcal/serving: 155

info.description: Serves 1 | A Chocolate lover's delight, made special with decadent Chocolate folded into 100% pure milk Rabdi slow-churned for hours. Kcal/serving: 166

info.name: Desi Malai Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | Our pack of 2 Kulfis, served in matkas, re-create the yester-years together. Enjoy these Desi Malai matkas made with special Rabdi slow-churned for hours. Kcal/serving: 195

info.name: Dry Fruit Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | Our pack of 2 Kulfis, served in matka pots, re-create the yester-years together. Enjoy these childhood desi blasts from the past, with chunky Pista & Almond folded into 100% Pure milk Rabdi. Kcal/serving: 224

info.name: Alphonso Mango Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | The crowning flavour of the fruit kingdom is now in the soothing company of the soulful matka, to deliver a tasteful experience that’s uniquely-delicious. Kcal/serving: 148

info.name: Kesar Pista Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | The very irresistible combination of saffron and green, combining two very complimenting flavours, for a uniquely-flavourful experience. Kcal/serving: 218

info.name: Thandai Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | A perfect tribute to the much-adored Indian treat of thandai, the thandai matka kulfi is a flavour that every desi dessert lover will unfailingly vouch for. Kcal/serving: 238

info.name: Shahi Gulkand Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | The rosy refreshment of Gulkand, served in the traditional matka, to make your day all the more special, no matter what the occasion is. Kcal/serving: 198

info.name: Gud Badaam Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Serves 1 | A very unique combination of two contrasting tastes – the sweet jiggery and the crunchy almond – served in the soothing matka. Kcal/serving: 208

info.name: Kesar Pista Slice Kulfi (pack Of 3)
info.description: Serves 1 | The goodness of Kesar, blended with the authentic Pista, to formulate a regal combination quite unlike any other. Experience it, to feel the difference. Kcal/serving: 224

info.name: Desi Malai Slice Kulfi (pack Of 3)
info.description: Serves 1 | Pack of 3 Kulfi slices bundled for every occasion big or small! Enjoy our Desi Malai Kulfi in all its glory, 1 is just not be enough! Kcal/serving: 215

info.name: Gulkand+ Malai Jugalbandi Slice Kulfi (pack Of 3)
info.description: Serves 1 | 2 in 1 Kulfis are a careful balance of taste & flavour with the best of both worlds put together. Enjoy our Desi Malai & Gulkand Kulfi Jugalbandi. Kcal/serving: 206

info.name: Malai Mela
info.description: Celebrate the festival of flavors with our rich Desi Malai trio: Stick, Slice, and Matka. Each bite is a creamy, comforting reminder of classic Indian celebrations!

info.name: Swaad Platter
info.description: A regal treat for the senses! Desi Malai Maha Matka, Chocolate Stick, and Kesar Pista Stick Kulfi come together to bring you an indulgent trio of richness, perfect for any festive gathering.

info.name: Delight Darbar
info.description: Dive into a royal spread with Desi Malai Matka, Kesar Pista Slice, and Alphonso Mango No Added Sugar Stick Kulfis. A vibrant, colorful tribute to Indian festivities and joyous moments!

info.name: Cheeni Kam
info.description: An all-natural, premium treat, this No Added Sugar combo features Desi Malai, Dry Fruit Matka, Desi Malai No Added Sugar Stick, and Kesar Pista No Added Sugar Stick. Every bite is a celebration of health, tradition, and pure pleasure.

info.name: Meetha Mazaa
info.description: Experience festival magic with the unique tastes of Calcutta Paan, Shahi Gulkand, Anjeer, and Gud Badam. These flavors capture the essence of India’s most beloved mithais, perfect for sharing festive joy!

info.name: No Added Sugar Desi Malai Stick Kulfi 70ml
info.description: A creamy classic made with no added sugar, perfect for savouring without guilt.

info.name: No Added Sugar Alphonso Mango Stick Kulfi 70ml
info.description: Experience the king of fruits in a Stick Kulfi, crafted with no added sugar for pure indulgence.

info.name: No Added Sugar Kesar Pista Stick Kulfi 70ml
info.description: Enjoy the royal blend of Kesar and Pista, made with no added sugar for a wholesome treat.

info.name: No Added Sugar Desi Malai Slice Kulfi (pack Of 3)
info.description: Rich and creamy Malai slices, made with no added sugar to maintain the authentic taste.

info.name: No Added Sugar Desi Malai Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Enjoy the rich, velvety texture of Malai Kulfi, made with no added sugar for a naturally smooth and satisfying treat.

info.name: No Added Sugar Dry Fruit Matka Kulfi (pack Of 2)
info.description: Packed with nutty dry fruits, this Matka Kulfi comes with no added sugar, making it indeed delicious.

info.name: Desi Malai Maha Matka Kulfi 500 Ml
info.description: A Maha delicious serving of Malai Kulfi for all your grand celebrations.Packed in a reusable limited edition collectible ceramic claypot.

info.name: Gaon Ka Swad
info.description: The perfect treat for fans of kulfi! Slice, Stick, and Matka are three delectable avatars that allow you to experience the creamy joy of Desi Malai. A regal delight for your palate!

info.name: Garmi Ka Jadoo
info.description: A regal getaway for the summer! Kesar Pista Slice Kulfi's golden richness, Shahi Gulkand Stick Kulfi's floral beauty and Gud Badam Stick Kulfi's earthy sweetness combine to create a kulfi experience that is absolutely regal.

info.name: Desi Daawat
info.description: Let the magic of summer unfold with this refreshing mix of kulfis! From the nutty crunch of Dry Fruit Matka Kulfi  to the tropical burst of Mango Matka Kulfi, the decadence of Chocolate Stick Kulfi, and the earthy charm of Anjeer Stick Kulfi. This combo is pure joy!

info.name: Mausam Ki Mithaas
info.description: Beat the heat with this cool blend of summertime favourites! Every taste is absolute delight, from the delicious Alphonso Mango Stick Kulfi to the rich NAS Kesar PistaStick Kulfi, buttery Butterscotch Stick Kulfi, and creamy NAS Desi Malai Stick Kulfi!

info.name: Malai Medley
info.description: Indulge in the creamy richness of our Malai Medley, featuring the classic flavors of Malai Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml), Malai Slice Kulfi (3 x 90ml), and Malai Matka Kulfi (2 x 100ml). Perfect for those who love the authentic taste of traditional kulfi.

info.name: Delightful Trio
info.description: Treat yourself to a delightful trio of exotic flavors with our Dry Fruit Matka Kulfi (2 x 100ml), Gulkand Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml), and Chocolate Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml). A perfect blend of richness, sweetness, and a hint of chocolatey goodness.

info.name: Royal Treat
info.description: Treat yourself to a delightful trio of exotic flavors with our Dry Fruit Matka Kulfi (2 x 100ml), Gulkand Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml), and Chocolate Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml). A perfect blend of richness, sweetness, and a hint of chocolatey goodness.

info.name: Flavors Of India
info.description: Experience the royal flavors of our Malai Slice Kulfi (3 x 90ml), Kesar Pista Slice Kulfi (3 x 90ml), and Anjeer Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml). This combo brings together the best of traditional Indian sweets in one irresistible package.

info.name: Fruity Bliss
info.description: Savor the fruity goodness with our Fruity Bliss combo. Enjoy the luscious Alphonso Mango Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml), crunchy Butterscotch Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml), aromatic Kesar Pista Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml), and nutritious Anjeer Stick Kulfi (1 x 70ml). Perfect for fruit and nut lovers!

info.description: Serves 1 | The creamy and rich custard apple delight, hard to resist and even harder to share. This is one flavour to be simply not missed, when the season arrives.
